  Amanda is a woman of many talents, with acting credits that include The Grimleys (1998–2001), Kiss Me Kate (1999–2001), Cutting It (2002–2004) and Wild at Heart (2006–2008). The fashion icon also played the title role in the musical stage show Thoroughly Modern Millie in 2004, for which she was nominated for a Laurence Olivier Award. She is probably best known for being a judge on the ITV television talent show competition Britain's Got Talent, which she has been a part of since 2007. She also co-hosts the Heart Breakfast radio show with Jamie Theakston on weekday mornings. Now, Express.co.uk takes a look back at 10 pictures of the star throughout her time in the spotlight.  